response_date.map: function(doc) {if (doc.type && doc.responses && doc.treatments && doc.triggers && doc.user_id && doc.date) {doc.responses.forEach(function(response) {var treatment_names = []; var triggers = []; doc.treatments.forEach(function(treatment) {treatment_names[treatment_names.length] = treatment.name;}); doc.triggers.forEach(function(trigger) {triggers[triggers.length] = trigger;}); emit([response.name, doc.date], [response.value, treatment_names, triggers, doc.user_id]);});}}

user_response.map: function(doc) {if (doc.type && doc.responses && doc.treatments && doc.triggers && doc.user_id && doc.date) {doc.responses.forEach(function(response) {var treatment_names = []; var triggers = []; doc.treatments.forEach(function(treatment) {treatment_names[treatment_names.length] = treatment.name;}); doc.triggers.forEach(function(trigger) {triggers[triggers.length] = trigger;}); emit([doc.user_id, response.name], [response.value, treatment_names, triggers, doc.date]);});}}
